The Faerie Wars Chronicles is a fantasy action young adult novel series written by James Herbert Brennan. The first book in the series, Faerie Wars was published in the United Kingdom in February 2003 by Bloomsbury Publishing. As of 2011, there are five books in the on-going series.Bloomsbury began releasing the series in the United States under its Bloomsbury USA imprint in April 2003. In January 2007, Macmillan Publishers began republishing the series in the United States under its Tor Books imprint. On January 16, 2005, the first novel in the series, Faerie Wars reached number 4 on the New York Times Best Seller list for paperback children's books.